snippet.title: SixTONES – Stargaze [YouTube ver.]
snippet.description:
「Stargaze」は、RADWIMPSの野田洋次郎さんによる書き下ろし楽曲。
詩的な言葉選びとドラマティックなサウンドが、SixTONES６名の力強くもエモーショナルな歌声と融合し、内なる情熱と”今”を生きる煌めきを描きながら、聴く人の背中を押す青春エールソング。

重力から解き放たれたように、空を舞い、風を裂き、景色を越えていく６人のメンバー。
現実と夢の境界を飛び越え"今"を生きる情熱が光になる。
CGとVFXを駆使したSixTONESの“今”を刻む映像詩が完成。

SixTONES
16th シングル「Stargaze」
2025.9.10 Release

「Stargaze」：日本テレビ系『高校生クイズ2025』応援ソング

-
Directed by YUANN / Kidzfrmnowhere
-

“Stargaze” is an original song written by Yojiro Noda of RADWIMPS.
It's poetic lyrics and dramatic sound blend seamlessly with the powerful and emotional voices of the six members of SixTONES, creating a vibrant anthem of youth.
The song captures the inner fire and brilliance of living in “the moment”, offering an uplifting push to everyone who listens.
--
The six members soar through the sky, slicing the wind and passing beyond landscapes, as if freed from the pull of gravity.
Their passion for living in “the moment” becomes a radiant light, transcending the boundary between reality and dreams.
A visual poem capturing SixTONES’ “now” has been brought to life with cutting-edge CG and VFX.
